textA <- scan("text A.txt",what = "",sep = "",na.strings = "NA")

textB <- scan("text B.txt",what = "",sep = "",na.strings = "NA")

textC <- scan("text C.txt",what = "",sep = "",na.strings = "NA")


douhaoA <- sum(str_detect(textA,","))

douhaoB <- sum(str_detect(textB,","))

douhaoC <- sum(str_detect(textC,","))

juhaoA <- sum(str_detect(textA,"\\."))

juhaoB <- sum(str_detect(textB,"\\."))

juhaoC <- sum(str_detect(textC,"\\."))

word <- c("may","might","would","will","maybe","can","could")

mayA <- 0
mayB <- 0
mayC <- 0
for(i in 1:length(word)){
    mayA <- mayA + sum(str_detect(textA,word[i]))
    mayB <- mayB + sum(str_detect(textB,word[i]))
    mayC <- mayC + sum(str_detect(textC,word[i]))

}

wordA <- length(textA)

wordB <- length(textB)

wordC <- length(textC)

meijuA <- wordA/juhaoA

meijuB <- wordB/juhaoB

meijuC <- wordC/juhaoC

mayA

mayB

mayC
